 The Girls’ Autumn Meeting held at Boyce Hill    Claudia Willmore (Thorpe Hall) winner of the Autumn
Meeting receives her prize from  County President, Bridget Logan       Georgina Blackman (Chelmsford) Scratch Winner receives her prize from
