from    

County
President, Bridget Logan   
 Final of the
Hunter Foursomes Trophy 2011 
 
 
 
 
 
 The
final of the Hunter Foursomes Trophy was played at Crondon Park Golf
Club.   
 
Amanda Colgate-Herbert and Shannon Wood
(Rochford Hundred) beat  Mandy
Grant and
Claudia Willmore (Thorpe Hall)  3
and 1. 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
   Winners Shannon Wood
and Amanda Colgate-Herbert with   
  
 runners-up Claudia Willmore
and Mandy Grant 
 
 
