 The
Alresford Cup 
      
 
 
 
 
 The Alresford
Cup was held on Sunday 2 nd  October and this
year nine counties took part and our team of girls were joint 4 th . 
 
 
 
  
     Back row:
Freya Noad, Gabriella Oxlade and Alice Hiluta   
 Front
row: Charlotte Deavin, Faye Trigg and Chelsea
Bernardine 
 
  
 West
Essex Retain Munro Shield 
 
 
 
 
 
 Gabriella
Cowley and Sophie Madden represented West Essex to retain the Munro
Foursomes
Shield after a closely fought match against Chelmsford at Colchester GC
on
Friday 30 th  September. 
A full
report of the final can be found under the Munro section. 
 
 
 
 
 

   
 Essex
golfers win Australian Spoons national final 
 
  
 
 
 
 
 Essex
golfers Gilly Cullen
and Brenda Lord from Clacton on Sea won the national final of the
Australian Spoons competition at Thorndon Park Golf Club. 
 
 
 
 
 
  
 
 
 
   
 
 
 
